narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: To anyone who wants to get better at the language.

This class is a pretty entertaining class and you will learn a lot. I know it is a struggle to go to class everyday but it really does help to continue to use the language. I would definitely advise for students to take the class.
I would recommend this course to any student who enjoys spanish and wants to continue taking spanish classes.

This class improves your Spanish skills dramatically. The professor is great, the material is relevant and within grasp, and the class will leave you much more comfortable with the language. I would definitely recommend this class to another student.
I would recommend the class. It was enjoyable if you are taking spanish.
